if there's no configure, only configure.ac then use autoconf to generate configure
compile fvwm2 need xorg-server-devel pkg-config xorg-server-devel libtool automake
installed that packages, and run `autoconf` will generate configure script

if autoconf get error about m4_patter_allow  then run
autoreconf -i -I /home/john/AUR/fvwm/fvwm-version-2_6_5/
./configure
make 
sudo make install

2.6.5 from github, compile successed!
